{"title_page": "2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic deaths/WHO situation reports", "text_new": "<noinclude>{{User:RMCD bot/subject notice|1=2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic deaths|2=Talk:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic cases/WHO situation reports#Requested move 29 March 2020 }}\n</noinclude>{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic sidebar}}\nFor a list of notable people who have died from Covid-19, see [[List of deaths from the 2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].\n{{Main|2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic|2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic cases/WHO situation reports}}\n\n==January 2020==\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"32\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"wikitable sortable\" align=\"center\"\n|+Coronavirus (SARS-CoV-2) cases in January 2020<ref group=\"notes\" name=\"scope\">This page summarises the deaths reported from the [[World Health Organization|WHO]] novel coronavirus ([[2019-nCoV]]) situation reports issued each day. For each country or territory, the table lists the number of confirmed deaths from novel coronavirus in total up to that point. The number of countries affected is shown, and the number of days it has taken for the number of cases to double. The table can be sorted by country or date of first confirmed case.</ref><ref name=whosituationreports>{{cite web|url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/situation-reports|title= Novel Coronavirus 2019 - Situation Updates|publisher=WHO|access-date= 23 March 2020}}</ref>\n!Date!!First reported case!!Jan&nbsp;19!!Jan&nbsp;20!!Jan&nbsp;21!!Jan&nbsp;22!!Jan&nbsp;23!!Jan&nbsp;24!!Jan&nbsp;25!!Jan&nbsp;26!!Jan&nbsp;27!!Jan&nbsp;28!!Jan&nbsp;29!!Jan&nbsp;30!!Jan&nbsp;31\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"\"      \"\" |World || || data-sort-value\"\"      \"\"|3||6||6||6||17||23||41||56||80||106||132||170||213\n|-\n| {{flag|China}} || {{Date table sorting|2020-1-19}} ||3||6||6||6||17||23||41||56||80||106||132||170||213\n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" |References\n|<ref>{{Citation|last=|first=|title=Novel Coronavirus (2